      "severity": "MAJOR-REVISION",
      "justification": "The manuscript repeatedly frames \\(\\mathcal F\\) as built from the same invariant building blocks as the golden relation, but no model is shown to generate this specific combination or the chosen scale/exponent structure. Without such a derivation, the connection to the cited flavor-symmetry literature is speculative; this weakens the central interpretation that the observation constitutes useful theoretical input rather than an isolated numerological coincidence."
    },
